00:17:22.600 --> 00:17:24.600
We don't break any rules.

00:17:24.600 --> 00:17:30.600
We don't, you know, go into drugs, into fights and things like this.

00:17:30.600 --> 00:17:36.600
Just live modest and peaceful and happy.

00:17:36.600 --> 00:17:38.600
I agree.

00:17:39.240 --> 00:17:45.240
