00:18:11.880 --> 00:18:15.880
But when we're together, we are as one.

00:18:15.880 --> 00:18:19.880
That's the way it's been.

00:18:19.880 --> 00:18:23.880
And I hope they keep it that way, don't divide.

00:18:23.880 --> 00:18:29.880
So that's one of the things to preserve, is to carry on the multicultural embracing of that.

00:18:29.880 --> 00:18:31.880
Very true.

00:18:32.520 --> 00:18:34.520
What type of things have you done in order?

00:18:34.520 --> 00:18:40.520
Do you still do to preserve and to carry on the multicultural connections?

00:18:40.520 --> 00:18:46.520
