00:18:56.520 --> 00:18:58.520
I'm not saying that.

00:18:59.160 --> 00:19:01.160
You can take the good in something and follow the right path.

00:19:01.160 --> 00:19:03.160
Because there's two paths in life.

00:19:03.160 --> 00:19:07.160
You can take the bad one, like I said to them, and you can take the good one.

00:19:07.160 --> 00:19:11.160
That is good friends and that is bad friends.

00:19:11.160 --> 00:19:15.160
So I've always teach them just follow the right way.

00:19:15.160 --> 00:19:17.160
And we'll go wrong then.

00:19:17.160 --> 00:19:19.160
I agree.

00:19:19.160 --> 00:19:23.160
